name: You Did It Faster Before
description:
A physics filled parkour speedrun through the clouds. With chickens. And bears. And rainbows.




Grapple, blink, leash, dagger throw, windblast and more as you quest to shave seconds off your time.

Use your abilities to improve your time and unlock even more powerful/silly abilities!

Made for 7DFPS 2020 by 

Evan Greenwood

Jason Sutherland

Of Free Lives
